title: Reese and Finch..... See you again
author: Team Rinch
comment: Ahhh!!! My heart!!  This is absolutely perfect. Thanks for sharing all those amazing Rinch scenes.  They will ALWAYS be the real Person of Interest to me.
This is so great. I feel sad and happy.
I was sobbing after this. Great show!!
"Sooner or later both of us will probably wind up dead." Finch.
